This project presents an **end-to-end Retail Analytics Case Study** built using **MySQL Workbench 8.0**, focusing on **data cleaning, customer segmentation, product performance analysis**, and **behavioral insights**.  
The goal is to help retail businesses **understand customer behavior**, **identify key revenue drivers**, and **support data-driven decision-making**.

